quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,35,"Nuko (uwo muhakanyi) yinjira mu murima we arihemukira (kubera kutemera no kwirata),agira ati \"Sinkeka ko ibi bizigera bishira"
  18,36,"Kandi sinkeka ko imperuka izigera ibaho! Ndetse (iramutse inabayeho) ngasubizwa kwa Nyagasani wanjye, rwose nzasangayo ibyiza biruta ibi"
  18,37,"Mugenzi we (w’umwemera) amubwira amuganiriza ati \"Ese urahakana uwakuremye mu gitaka (cyaremwemo umukurambere wawe Adam), hanyuma (akakurema) mu ntanga (z’ababyeyi), maze akagutunganya akakugira umuntu"
  18,38,"Ahubwo ku bwanjye, (uwakoze ibyo) ni Allah, Nyagasani wanjye, kandi ntawe nzigera mbangikanya na Nyagasani wanjye"
  18,39,"(Byari kuba byiza kuri wowe) iyo uza kwinjira mu murima wawe ugira uti \"Ibi ni ibyo Allah yanshoboje! Ntacyo nakwishoborera ku bwanjye bitari ku bushobozi bwa Allah. N’ubwo ubona ndi munsi yawe mu mutungo n’abana"
  18,40,"Hari ubwo Nyagasani wanjye yampa ibiruta umurima wawe, (maze uwawe) akawutezaikiza giturutse mu kirere, maze ugahinduka imbuga nsa inyerera"
  18,41,"Cyangwa amazi yawo (umurima) akarigita, ntuzashobore kuyagarura"
  18,42,"Nuko umurima we uterwa n’ikiza (kirawararika), maze asigara yimyiza imoso (abitewe n’agahinda) kubera ibyo yawutanzeho, (abonye ibihingwa) byagwiriranye aravuga ati \"Iyo nza kuba ntarabangikanyije Nyagasani wanjye n’uwo ari we wese"
  18,43,"Kandi ntiyigeze agira itsinda ry’abantu bamutabara (ngo bamurinde) ibihano bya Allah, ndetse na we ubwe ntiyashoboye kwitabara"
  18,44,"Mu bihe nk’ibyo, ubutabazi nyabwo buba ari ubwa Allah, Imana y’ukuri. Ni we uhebuje mu gutanga ingororano, ndetse ni na we uhebuje mu gutanga iherezo ryiza"
  18,45,"Bahe urugero rw’ubuzima bwo ku isi ko ari nk’amazi twamanuye mu kirere, akuhira ibimera byo ku isi (bigatohagira), ariko nyuma bikumagara, bigatumurwa n’umuyaga. Kandi Allah ni Ushobora byose"